@startuml
[*] --> Idle

Idle --> UpdatingDetails : update inventory details
UpdatingDetails --> Idle : details updated

Idle --> ProductStatusMonitoring : monitor product status
ProductStatusMonitoring --> ExchangeNeeded : expired items detected
ExchangeNeeded --> NotifyingDealers : notify dealers to exchange items

Idle --> SalesStrategyApplication : apply sales strategies
SalesStrategyApplication --> ApplyingDiscounts : discount applied to specific products

ProductStatusMonitoring --> Idle : no expired items found
SalesStrategyApplication --> Idle : no sales strategy change

ExchangeNeeded --> Idle : exchange completed
ApplyingDiscounts --> Idle : discount applied
@enduml
